{"tid":1099041,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"有冇人覺得D人成日夾硬加個黃金比例線去D相/畫到好ON9","createTime":"2019-04-09T13:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T15:16:55.000Z","uid":119409,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"efdcbaa9147013494a511258f40e886e94f698ef","tid":1099041,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"黃金比例係一個聲稱最令人眼覺得舒服自然嘅構圖比例<br />\nD人分析D相同畫果時成日加上去張圖到.話咩符合黃金比例<br />\n真係好ON9. 好多明明線線個位同實物張圖個距離係好遠<br />\n夾硬話係黃金比例所以好靚<br />\n係張圖到加條線，是但貼住條線果D野都講成係構圖<br />\n真係是但係街到鳩影十張8張都可以比你吹到係黃金比例嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1585ba6882c57ceeb6d2a5a4945a22ba2e5675ef","tid":1099041,"uid":119409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"明明話黃金比例係1/3...<br />\n然後個實物例子就係1/2<br />\n仆街差咁遠都用黎論證.<br />\n咁係咪證明你覺得佢靚唔關個比例事呢?<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nAFMQHvK2PQ/Ti1WkX2aweI/AAAAAAAAMgM/19qZjKVi3Mo/s1600/GoldenM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-nAFMQHvK2PQ%2FTi1WkX2aweI%2FAAAAAAAAMgM%2F19qZjKVi3Mo%2Fs1600%2FGoldenM.jpg&h=e5ccd4f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf97ef3fa7dedc902cdf0d913c0004776306c37c","tid":1099041,"uid":119409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"又成日拎鸚鵡螺黎講<br />\n明明泊上去條線係完全走晒位<br />\n個比例都差好遠<br />\n只係個形狀比較似<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT7oRAy8YVv_7pzBbWym7yHAjg7iqxHbrhOEgRpHwRAPQh--a08KA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcT7oRAy8YVv_7pzBbWym7yHAjg7iqxHbrhOEgRpHwRAPQh--a08KA&h=00ce6ff2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"111fa2fa2dd61b39cd7264afe55f53a9750f7b09","tid":1099041,"uid":119409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.catsbro.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/fibonacci-composition-cats-furbonacci-url-7_